  "rationale": {
    "description": "Embedded system is one of the rapidly growing technologies in the era of automation. In current scenario, Internet of Things (IoT) & Industrial IoT platforms are evolving at rapid pace. To develop such platforms and applications, students need to have deep understanding about embedded hardware and software systems. This course is intended to provide insights about fundamentals of embedded systems hardware as well as software which are essential for IoT, automation and control system development.",
    "industryRelevance": "The course prepares students for careers in embedded systems development, IoT platform development, automation industry, and control systems engineering.",
    "academicRelevance": "Builds foundation for advanced topics in IoT, real-time systems, and embedded software engineering."
  },
